  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The following contains clips from Disney's Frozen and Frozen 2.",
      "zh": "以下包含迪士尼《冰雪奇緣》和《冰雪奇緣2》的片段。",
      "ja": "以下はディズニーの『アナと雪の女王』と『アナと雪の女王2』のクリップを含みます。",
      "time": "00:00:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Now available on Blue Ray and DVD.",
      "zh": "現已在藍光和DVD發行。",
      "ja": "ブルーレイとDVDで発売中です。",
      "time": "00:00:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Pulse and power!",
      "zh": "脈動與力量！",
      "ja": "パルスとパワー！",
      "time": "00:00:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Whoa.",
      "zh": "哇。",
      "ja": "おおっと。",
      "time": "00:00:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm a place you're sled, and everything in it.",
      "zh": "我是一個你滑雪橇的地方，和裡面的一切。",
      "ja": "私はあなたがそりをする場所であり、その中のすべてです。",
      "time": "00:00:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And I understand if you don't want to help me anymore.",
      "zh": "如果你不想再幫助我，我也能理解。",
      "ja": "もう私を助けたくないなら、それも理解します。",
      "time": "00:00:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Of course I don't want to help her anymore.",
      "zh": "當然我不想再幫助她了。",
      "ja": "もちろん、もう彼女を助けたくありません。",
      "time": "00:00:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "In fact, this whole thing has ruined me for helping anyone ever again.",
      "zh": "事實上，這整件事讓我再也不想幫助任何人了。",
      "ja": "実際、この一件で私はもう誰も助けたくなくなりました。",
      "time": "00:00:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So die on her own!",
      "zh": "那就讓她自己去死吧！",
      "ja": "じゃあ彼女は自分で死ねばいい！",
      "time": "00:00:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I can live with that.",
      "zh": "我能接受這點。",
      "ja": "それなら私は構いません。",
      "time": "00:00:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "But you won't get your new sled if she's dead.",
      "zh": "但如果她死了，你就拿不到你的新雪橇。",
      "ja": "でも彼女が死んだら、新しいそりは手に入らないよ。",
      "time": "00:00:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Sometimes I really don't like you.",
      "zh": "有時候我真的不喜歡你。",
      "ja": "時々、本当に君のことが嫌いになる。",
      "time": "00:00:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, hold up! We're coming!",
      "zh": "喔，等等！我們來了！",
      "ja": "おっと、待って！今行くよ！",
      "time": "00:00:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What? I mean, sure!",
      "zh": "什麼？我是說，當然！",
      "ja": "え？ああ、もちろん！",
      "time": "00:00:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Sure! Yeah, I'll let you tag along.",
      "zh": "當然！是的，我讓你一起來。",
      "ja": "いいよ！一緒に来ていいよ。",
      "time": "00:00:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "zh": "喔，對。",
      "ja": "ああ、そうだね。",
      "time": "00:01:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "zh": "喔，對。",
      "ja": "ああ、そうだね。",
      "time": "00:01:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "zh": "喔，對。",
      "ja": "ああ、そうだね。",
      "time": "00:01:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I never knew winter could be so beautiful.",
      "zh": "我從不知道冬天可以這麼美麗。",
      "ja": "冬がこんなに美しいなんて知らなかった。",
      "time": "00:01:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "是啊。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:01:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "zh": "喔，對。",
      "ja": "ああ、そうだね。",
      "time": "00:01:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I never knew winter could be so beautiful.",
      "zh": "我從不知道冬天可以這麼美麗。",
      "ja": "冬がこんなに美しいなんて知らなかった。",
      "time": "00:01:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "是啊。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:01:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It really is beautiful, isn't it?",
      "zh": "真的很美，不是嗎？",
      "ja": "本当に美しいよね？",
      "time": "00:01:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "But so...",
      "zh": "但是...",
      "ja": "でも...",
      "time": "00:01:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Alright, take a nice walk.",
      "zh": "好，去散個步吧。",
      "ja": "よし、いい散歩をしてきて。",
      "time": "00:01:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Good work.",
      "zh": "做得好。",
      "ja": "よくやった。",
      "time": "00:01:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I gotcha.",
      "zh": "我抓住你了。",
      "ja": "捕まえたよ。",
      "time": "00:01:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay. You stay right here, buddy.",
      "zh": "好。你就在這裡待著，夥伴。",
      "ja": "いいよ。ここにいてね、相棒。",
      "time": "00:01:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Floss.",
      "zh": "牙線。",
      "ja": "フロス。",
      "time": "00:01:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay. Okay. Here we are.",
      "zh": "好，好，我們到了。",
      "ja": "はい、はい。ここだよ。",
      "time": "00:01:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh.",
      "zh": "喔。",
      "ja": "ああ。",
      "time": "00:01:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I owe you a sled.",
      "zh": "我欠你一台雪橇。",
      "ja": "そりを借りてるよ。",
      "time": "00:01:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, no.",
      "zh": "喔，不。",
      "ja": "ああ、いやだ。",
      "time": "00:02:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Are you serious?",
      "zh": "你是認真的嗎？",
      "ja": "本気？",
      "time": "00:02:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "In its the latest model.",
      "zh": "這是最新款。",
      "ja": "これは最新モデルだよ。",
      "time": "00:02:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No, I can't accept this.",
      "zh": "不，我不能接受這個。",
      "ja": "いや、これは受け取れない。",
      "time": "00:02:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You have to. No returns.",
      "zh": "你必須收下。不能退貨。",
      "ja": "受け取らなきゃ。返品不可。",
      "time": "00:02:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No exchanges. Queen's orders. She's named you the official Arindale Ice Master and deliverer.",
      "zh": "不能換貨。女王的命令。她任命你為阿林戴爾官方冰雪大師和送貨員。",
      "ja": "交換不可。女王の命令だ。君はアリンダールの公式アイスマスター兼配達人に任命された。",
      "time": "00:02:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What? That's not a thing.",
      "zh": "什麼？那不是什麼職位。",
      "ja": "え？そんなものはないよ。",
      "time": "00:02:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Don't sure it is, and it even has a cup holder.",
      "zh": "不確定是不是，但它還有杯架。",
      "ja": "あるかどうかはわからないけど、カップホルダーも付いてるよ。",
      "time": "00:02:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Do you like it?",
      "zh": "你喜歡嗎？",
      "ja": "気に入った？",
      "time": "00:02:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Like it.",
      "zh": "喜歡。",
      "ja": "好きだよ。",
      "time": "00:02:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I love it!",
      "zh": "我愛它！",
      "ja": "大好き！",
      "time": "00:02:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, wow!",
      "zh": "喔，哇！",
      "ja": "おお、わあ！",
      "time": "00:02:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hello.",
      "zh": "哈囉。",
      "ja": "こんにちは。",
      "time": "00:02:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm tired too.",
      "zh": "我也累了。",
      "ja": "私も疲れたよ。",
      "time": "00:02:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And Sven promised to read me a bedtime story.",
      "zh": "而且斯文答應要給我念睡前故事。",
      "ja": "それにスヴェンが寝る前の話を読んでくれるって約束した。",
      "time": "00:02:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Didn't you, Sven?",
      "zh": "不是嗎，斯文？",
      "ja": "そうだよね、スヴェン？",
      "time": "00:02:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Did I?",
      "zh": "我有嗎？",
      "ja": "そうだったかな？",
      "time": "00:02:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, you do the best voices.",
      "zh": "喔，你的配音最好聽了。",
      "ja": "ああ、君の声真に上手だよね。",
      "time": "00:02:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Like when you pretend to be Christophe and you're like,",
      "zh": "就像你假裝是克里斯托夫時說，",
      "ja": "クリストフのふりをして、こんな感じで言う時みたいに、",
      "time": "00:02:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I just need to go talk to some rocks about my childhood in school.",
      "zh": "我只是需要去跟一些石頭談談我在學校的童年。",
      "ja": "学校での子供時代について岩に話しかける必要があるんだ。",
      "time": "00:03:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Water has memory.",
      "zh": "水有記憶。",
      "ja": "水には記憶がある。",
      "time": "00:03:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The water that makes up you and me has passed through at least four humans and animals before us.",
      "zh": "構成你我身體的水，曾經流經至少四個人類和動物。",
      "ja": "君と私を構成する水は、私たちの前に少なくとも4人の人間と動物を通ってきた。",
      "time": "00:03:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And from that verse everything.",
      "zh": "從那節經文中，一切皆來。",
      "ja": "そしてその詩からすべてが生まれた。",
      "time": "00:03:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The band's back.",
      "zh": "樂隊回來了。",
      "ja": "バンドが戻ってきた。",
      "time": "00:03:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Delicious.",
      "zh": "美味。",
      "ja": "美味しい。",
      "time": "00:03:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, I am on a primary and a secondary.",
      "zh": "喔，我在主線和支線上。",
      "ja": "ああ、私は主線と副線にいる。",
      "time": "00:03:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm just gonna blow.",
      "zh": "我要吹了。",
      "ja": "吹き飛ばすよ。",
      "time": "00:03:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Slope, no.",
      "zh": "斜坡，不。",
      "ja": "斜面、ダメ。",
      "time": "00:03:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Magic pulses through my snowflakes.",
      "zh": "魔法在我的雪花中脈動。",
      "ja": "魔法が私の雪の結晶を通り抜ける。",
      "time": "00:03:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I live.",
      "zh": "我活著。",
      "ja": "私は生きている。",
      "time": "00:03:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ice Palace for one.",
      "zh": "冰宮一人份。",
      "ja": "アイスパレス一人用。",
      "time": "00:03:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Ice Palace for one.",
      "zh": "冰宮一人份。",
      "ja": "アイスパレス一人用。",
      "time": "00:03:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Get out on a new new my heart.",
      "zh": "走出我的新心。",
      "ja": "新しい私の心に出て行け。",
      "time": "00:03:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh my goodness.",
      "zh": "天哪。",
      "ja": "なんてこった。",
      "time": "00:03:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What the an act of true love can save you.",
      "zh": "真正的愛能拯救你。",
      "ja": "真実の愛の行為が君を救う。",
      "time": "00:03:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Here's a true love's kiss.",
      "zh": "這是真愛之吻。",
      "ja": "これが真実の愛のキスだ。",
      "time": "00:03:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You're not worth it.",
      "zh": "你不值得。",
      "ja": "君はそれに値しない。",
      "time": "00:03:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Guess what? I'm the bad guy.",
      "zh": "猜猜看？我是壞人。",
      "ja": "なんだと思う？僕が悪者だ。",
      "time": "00:03:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What?",
      "zh": "什麼？",
      "ja": "え？",
      "time": "00:03:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Anna, you are the most extraordinary person I've ever known.",
      "zh": "安娜，你是我認識過最特別的人。",
      "ja": "アナ、君は僕が今まで知った中で最も特別な人だ。",
      "time": "00:03:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I love you with all I am.",
      "zh": "我全心全意愛你。",
      "ja": "僕は全ての自分をもって君を愛している。",
      "time": "00:03:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Will you marry me?",
      "zh": "你願意嫁給我嗎？",
      "ja": "結婚してくれますか？",
      "time": "00:03:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Nice.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "いいね。",
      "time": "00:03:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh.",
      "zh": "喔。",
      "ja": "ああ。",
      "time": "00:04:01"
